{"tid":645851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★華北驚現帶白色尾光UFO？","createTime":"2018-04-28T13:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T15:08:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5c9833fdb6abc5a987fff3c948ee7387b280f87b","tid":645851,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T13:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180428/photo/bkncn-20180428093341167-0428_05011_001_01b.jpg?20180428213714\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180428%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180428093341167-0428_05011_001_01b.jpg%3F20180428213714&h=a9fd4f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180428/photo/bkncn-20180428093341167-0428_05011_001_02b.jpg?20180428213714\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180428%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180428093341167-0428_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20180428213714&h=f1e3e616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地驚現不明飛行物體（UFO）？北京、天津、山西、內蒙古等華北地區民眾，周五（27日）晚上紛紛表示看到疑似UFO。該不明物拖着白色長扇形尾光，猶如巨型電筒，在高空中劃過曲線，維持數分鐘後才消失。UFO照片在網上瘋傳，網民對此眾説紛紜，紛紛猜測是飛碟、導彈或火箭。內地專家推測，可能是高超音速飛行器、小型火箭或小衞星。惟中科院引述專家分析指，市民所見實為夜光雲版本的航迹雲。<br />\n<br />\n華北地區多個省區市民眾，前晚都目擊這個不明飛行物體，並在網上發布大量相片及短片。據河南周口市的網民形容，看到天空西北方向有一道亮光，並拖着長長的尾巴。有民眾指出，不明飛行物有一道扇形亮光，遂戲言：「誰把手電筒扔到天上了？」<br />\n<br />\n內地航空專家王亞男當晚8時在北京科技大學目擊事件，估計該不明物在天空高度超過8千米，沒有發出聲音，判斷為人造飛行器，亦可能為火箭和導彈。中國導彈技術專家、核戰略專家楊承軍則認為，該飛行物的角度很小，拐彎很急且靈活，判斷飛行物可能為長度在兩米內的小型火箭、帶有動力的小衞星，或者其他用於科學探測的小衞星。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180428/bkncn-20180428093341167-0428_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180428%2Fbkncn-20180428093341167-0428_05011_001.html&d=U4%2BlvUUDs5%2Fc0dKtW0k%2Bnv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=515ec78b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180428/bkncn-20180428093341167-0428_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"72770309e0a0266dd3575875da36cf56ff080011","tid":645851,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T13:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2defa507fb9ce5acb6c51bea59ecd440aeee40f","tid":645851,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"外星人來支那取回一切版權？"},{"pid":"497cc65e688dfb006caf2b73100a2aa357655390","tid":645851,"uid":109701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:01:14.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5f21454233afdcfe6bd9e2fe7fa2673f1eb106","tid":645851,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"火箭吖"},{"pid":"1331b20cb1a53f9ea295073698702fd11f5b7336","tid":645851,"uid":18127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:30:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9264577bc8a4fa543b697c9197a513eccd5dde4","tid":645851,"uid":2736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bc0304c3166cd811276b9be62a60bceeceb3512","tid":645851,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1d397d2f3678eae7aa78235db8702970854a1e","tid":645851,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"出現在中國,  中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126d772ab337333c7d3280d0d223e50b0bddda33","tid":645851,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:01:04.000Z","msg":"星期一跌幾多"},{"pid":"c2132fc46bc7e06b4102d65a6eb76a7e842579ad","tid":645851,"uid":78968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"左上張圖好似飲左大頭奶粉嘅精蟲"},{"pid":"2da61027682d5a297cc421ae8ffdfd1c7f0d18d6","tid":645851,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"有人話係試導彈"},{"pid":"41363a89e62a33f3b90b3955d0be4eccec5d3c00","tid":645851,"uid":167574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:05:04.000Z","msg":"中國或成...."},{"pid":"d45fa5169833dfd4f2c0a6ada4bd5f1ebfdb480b","tid":645851,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ycSTghqQo4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FycSTghqQo4Y&d=U4%2BlvUUDs5%2Fc0dKtW0k%2Bnv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=4642f9c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ycSTghqQo4Y</a>"},{"pid":"c05552f40d961cfbf6f1c5f2223ef0b7f21502cb","tid":645851,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:07:38.000Z","msg":"支那射嘢失敗，但最後都係贏咗"},{"pid":"d26e3acc48593e2ed678219c00a9e88e9f648350","tid":645851,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2defa507fb9ce5acb6c51bea59ecd440aeee40f","tid":645851,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"外星人來支那取回一切版權？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:07:53.000Z","msg":"收到風外星人敗訴"},{"pid":"e662073106c3bb64da1a5f66399db24d986439e3","tid":645851,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"【看中國2018年4月28日訊】（看中國記者林中宇綜合報導）4月27日，中國北方多地出現在高空變軌的「不明飛行物」，這被指屬中國軍方進行的軍事活動，很可能是一次導彈測試，與中美軍事暗中較量有關。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體4月28日報導，4月27日大陸高空出現的「不明飛行物」，天津、北京、山西等地均有目擊記錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有猜測指是中國進行的一次衛星發射活動，或是北斗衛星發射。不過中國《科技日報》稱，北斗衛星從來都是從四川的西昌衛星發射中心發射，而太原衛星發射中心近期無發射任務。<br />\n<br />\n由於「不明飛行物」不斷變軌，也有猜測認為是中國軍方進行的一次軍事活動，特別是反導攔截測試。畢竟，中國此前的反導攔截測試地點之一就包括山西五寨導彈測試基地。<br />\n<br />\n《多維網》分析稱，中國曾進行的反導攔截測試中的靶彈多從山西五寨發射，穿越陝西、甘肅、青海，一路向西至新疆且末靶場，攔截彈則多從甘肅、青海等地發射，雷達測控設施則地處新疆庫爾勒。因而過往的「不明飛行物」多常見於前述多地。如果此次天津、北京等地的「不明飛行物」屬同類行動，則意味著這與此前的反導攔截測試路徑不同。<br />\n<br />\n也有消息說，可能是中國海軍094型戰略核潛艇在渤海進行潛射彈道導彈測試活動。此前，遼寧海事局在4月20日曾發布一則航行警告，地點位於渤海北部的葫蘆島外海，時間跨度在4月20日至28日。而葫蘆島正是中國核潛艇生產測試基地。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.secretchina.com/news/b5/2018/04/28/857051.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F857051.html&d=U4%2BlvUUDs5%2Fc0dKtW0k%2Bnv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=833bef84\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.secretchina.com/news/b5/2018/04/28/857051.html</a>"},{"pid":"782a0143ddb46884c0d36236a08e0912aa93e3b4","tid":645851,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:08:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EGOaHm0s6Es\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEGOaHm0s6Es&d=U4%2BlvUUDs5%2Fc0dKtW0k%2Bnv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=00f9a1a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EGOaHm0s6Es</a><br />\n一樣原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}